 red;\">不代表買家已經知道物業有僭建物</span>。<br />\n<br />\n最搞笑係似乎係同一個律師"},{"pid":"f6bf26501978dcfbc02c20df30709a282e1d2e34","tid":521754,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T22:49:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b18391bdd1f18fe52d2c59989de3d8be7205387d","tid":521754,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T22:51:04.000Z","msg":"玩野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaedc6657f7cb3a93b5843a3a2b01c8f7330e87","tid":521754,"uid":158075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T23:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淫媒要下馬威<br />\n今次擺明夾埋做9新師長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有線話 唔代表佢知喎 點會係做鳩佢"},{"pid":"b80a478801ca8fd6fc290c446a5e04abf149e641","tid":521754,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T23:13:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfc5a67a17f1720ca1386455380d6262aa749ef5","tid":521754,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n精彩"}]}